%% Diagram: Failure handling decision tree for transcoding jobs
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TB
    F[Job failure] --> Q1{Failure class?}
    Q1 -->|Transient| R1[Retry w/ backoff]
    Q1 -->|Resource OOM| R2[Retry on larger box]
    Q1 -->|Permanent| DLQ[Dead-letter queue]
    Q1 -->|Non-idempotent| FAIL[Fail - do not retry]
    R1 --> Q2{Attempts left?}
    R2 --> Q2
    Q2 -->|Yes| RUN[Re-enqueue]
    Q2 -->|No| DLQ
    DLQ --> ALERT[Alert + manual triage]
    FAIL --> ALERT
